<doc id="339441" wikidata="Q1938451" url="?curid=339441" title="Pygomeles trivittatus">
<text>Pygomeles trivittatus is a skink in the (family Scincidae). It appeared to be nested within the monotypic genus &quot;Androngo&quot;, but this species more recently was found to be more closely related to &quot;Pygomeles&quot;.

