<text>is a Japanese manga artist. He is best known for his series &quot;Saikano&quot; (&quot;She, the Ultimate Weapon&quot;) and &quot;Kimi no Kakera&quot;. Inio Asano had a brief stint as his assistant during the creation of &quot;Saikano&quot;.

